    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Here is <i>some </i>features about this game and the concept!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Overview:</strong> <br>Welcome to &quot;The Last Customer,&quot; a gripping survival horror experience set in an isolated gas station. As Mike, the dedicated clerk, you and your missing friend John face nightmarish beings disguised as customers. Your mission: identify who’s there for gas and who has deadly intentions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Story:</strong><br>The gas station, once a safe haven, is now haunted by grotesque monsters. With John mysteriously absent, Mike must navigate a chilling night filled with deceit. As reality blurs with nightmare, will he find John and survive, or become the next victim?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Gameplay Features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Interactive Storytelling:</strong> Your choices shape the narrative and influence outcomes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249630/extras/39b2ab421a87c57f1d88894414998a6c.avif?t=1729854017\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249630/extras_big/39b2ab421a87c57f1d88894414998a6c.avif?t=1729854017 width=800 height=412 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Identify the Threat:</strong> Use your instincts to distinguish between harmless customers and deadly monsters.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Atmospheric Horror:</strong> Experience a tense environment filled with dark corners and chilling visuals.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249630/extras/f6029359a970079a41be6d1857f10633.avif?t=1729854017\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249630/extras_big/f6029359a970079a41be6d1857f10633.avif?t=1729854017 width=800 height=414 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Multiple Endings:</strong> Your decisions lead to various outcomes—will you escape or succumb to the terror?</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Real-Time Decision Making:</strong> Quick judgments are crucial for survival.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Dynamic AI:</strong> Monsters adapt, keeping you on edge.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249630/extras/56902c39223b7ba5f5ad26fe0e1b4fdc.avif?t=1729854017\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249630/extras_big/56902c39223b7ba5f5ad26fe0e1b4fdc.avif?t=1729854017 width=800 height=408 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Psychological Horror:</strong> Fear that challenges your sanity with subtle cues and unexpected moments.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>You Can Play It On A CRT:</strong> Its Aspect ratio is 4:3/1.33 </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In &quot;The Last Customer,&quot; trust no one and fear everyone. Can you survive the night and uncover the truth? Step into Mike’s shoes and prepare for relentless suspense and terror.</p>",
